  "name": "Nagaraja COU1 — Non-cannulated pedicle screw compression-bending credibility assessment (Minimal profile)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for FEA prediction of ASTM F1717 static compression-bending performance of a non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw construct intended for lumbar spinal fixation in adult patients. The FEA model ensemble (FDA, Ansys, DePuy Synthes) is compared against N=11 experimental constructs across two independent laboratories. All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors have been assessed; one factor (Test conditions) is below the required level due to a single test condition being evaluated. The intended use is limited to static structural prediction under ASTM F1717 boundary conditions and does not extend to fatigue, dynamic loading, or in vivo biomechanical simulation.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/nagaraja-f1717-compression-bending-req",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/synth/claim/nagaraja-fea-predicts-f1717-stiffness-and-yield",
  "bindsModel": "https://uofa.net/synth/model/nagaraja-pedicle-screw-fea-ensemble",
